                  </hi> he man could not have reached it where the boy described it to be—I swear no other person but the prisoner went up the chimney—the boy was sweeping the front parlour chimney, but I did not</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183506150025"></xptr>
               <p>leave the place for more than five minutes, before I heard the purse was missed—the man was taken, but discharged.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I went to sweep up the hearth and found the thimble—I put it into my aide pocket—I never saw the purse.</p>
